  "texts": [
    "Current State.",
    "Existing LMA systems, such as ChatDev [109], MetaGPT [48], and AgileCoder [101], effectively simulate roles like generic software developers and product managers.",
    "The agents in these systems rely on general-purpose LLMs such as ChatGPT.",
    "Although LLMs like ChatGPT exhibit strong programming skills, they still lack the nuanced expertise required in SE [50].",
    "This limitation hampers their ability to simulate other SE-specific roles."
  ]
}